[Amit Varma]: And it's not like there is one federation, the federation which created this kind of

01:44:35.160 --> 01:44:39.080
[Amit Varma]: poker was something called the International Federation of Match Poker and match poker

01:44:39.080 --> 01:44:43.120
[Amit Varma]: is not poker, which is why I kind of came out of I was a poker player for five years

