[Guest 1]: now, but the concept of social distancing was quite popular at the time.

01:56:36.200 --> 01:56:41.640
[Guest 1]: And sport was seen as a way of socially distancing yourself from sort of the plebeians to show

01:56:41.640 --> 01:56:46.760
[Guest 1]: that you were anglicized and sort of with it and cool for the time.

01:56:46.760 --> 01:56:52.160
[Guest 1]: So a lot of the sports are around that and then that whole notion of privilege and sport.

